---
title: Vietnamese Chicken 'Bun Cha' with Pickled Veggies and Vermicelli Noodles
description: This traditional Vietnamese dish was a huge hit in our test kitchen! From the moist, easy -to-make chicken patties , to the sweet tangy spice of  the dipping sauce and the no-fuss vermicelli rice noodles, we added extra fragrant herbs to round out this taste sensation. Satisfying in so many ways!
